## Prison Riot Event
station-event-bluespace-prison-riot-incoming = Long-range sensors have detected a prison transport vessel experiencing catastrophic containment failure. Estimated arrival: 30 minutes. All SLE Officers should prepare for riot control operations. The SLE is authorized for NON-LETHAL force only! Police budgets will be provided bonus funds for all prisoners alive and in cuffs when the Colonial Navy takes possession of the vessel. Medics may recover wounded guards for patient recovery rewards.
station-event-bluespace-prison-riot-arrived = Alert! The prison transport vessel has arrived - SLE officers are ordered to de-escalate the situation. There is a 300m NFZ around this active combat zone.
station-event-bluespace-prison-riot-warning = Warning: Colonial Navy are preparing to take the vessel. Five minutes remain to secure all prisoners before hand-off.
station-event-bluespace-prison-riot-end = The prison vessel has departed the sector. Bonuses are being tallied and rewarded where applicable.

## Smuggler Interception Event
station-event-bluespace-smuggler-interception-incoming = Long-range sensors have detected a heavily-armed vessel that just raided a government supply transport. Estimated arrival: 15 minutes. All SLE Officers should prepare for hostile engagement. Lethal force is AUTHORIZED and will likely be REQUIRED.  For every recovered crate, and complete neutralization of the crew, bonuses will be awarded to the SLE budget.
station-event-bluespace-smuggler-interception-arrived = Alert! The smuggler vessel has arrived in-sector. The SLE is ordered to engage, and recover the cargo. The crew of this vessel is armed and hostile, with stated intent to shoot to kill. There is a 300m NFZ around this active combat zone.
station-event-bluespace-smuggler-interception-warning = Warning: Smuggler vessel FTL systems are charging. Five minutes remain to neutralize crew and secure contraband before departure.
station-event-bluespace-smuggler-interception-end = The smuggler vessel has departed the sector. Bonuses are being tallied and rewarded where applicable.

